channel.title: Help! how do i turn auto kicker off so i dont get kicked when i dont move
channel.description:
HELLO IM NEW AT THIS AND IM HAVING SOME TROUBLE I DONT KNOW HOW TO TURN THE AUTO KICKER OFF WHEN I LOG ON AND DONT MOVE MY MOUSE IT KICKS ME HOW DO I TURN IT OFF PLEASE HELP OR TELL ME A LINK TO GO TO
THANKS :)

item.title: Help! how do i turn auto kicker off so i dont get kicked when i dont move
item.dc:creator: @airforce711 airforce711
item.description:
@airforce711 wrote:

Open up Client.Java in your server files.
Hit Ctrl + f Search for

case 202: Maybe 200.

You should see this case 202: // idle logout packet if(!inCombat) logout(); break;
Simply erase it, what i did.
